{"tid":2068851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普回應要求中共助選傳聞指從沒有人較他更強硬應對中國","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:44:55.000Z","uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30f5293ea9c58707422b5c0ac3fa7ac8c2a2a7b1","tid":2068851,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"特朗普指從沒有人較他更強硬應對中國<br />\n18.06.2020 11:02<br />\n<br />\n美國前白宮國家安全顧問博爾頓即將出版的新書，披露總統特朗普曾懇求國家主席習近平幫助他連任。特朗普接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，對於中國，無人比他更強硬，可以從中國賺取數以十億美元計的關稅。他又再次批評博爾頓違反法律，指新書內容涉及高度機密資料，博爾頓未有獲准就公開，已經給他機會。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓在書中指，指去年6月特朗普在大阪出席20國集團峰會期間與習近平會面，暗示中國的經濟實力能影響美國總統大選的選情，懇求習近平確保他能連任，又指中國增購美國大豆及小麥，能影響選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312850&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1312850%26csid%3D261_367&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a061d174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312850&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"f19862d1ee4c628455835d4fb86a1de04b1c4b42","tid":2068851,"uid":55955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"今年大選主題就係鬥強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2e636470a539d450bdcd7ce2d62d9b01313fb5","tid":2068851,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqZFQ4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqZFQ4Q.jpg&h=f39bffda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29w1Aww.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29w1Aww.gif&h=0c21f4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打佢老母閪"},{"pid":"bae47b426b18ccd0c00b61d18890c54bb9ab3b24","tid":2068851,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:47:1